def determine_election_winner(n, m, votes):
    city_wins = [0] / n
    for city_votes in votes:
        winner_index = city_votes.index(max(city_votes))
        city_wins[winner_index] += 1
    overall_winner_index = city_wins.index(max(city_wins))
    return overall_winner_index + 1
